claim.claim-text:
A method for controlling a mobile terminal, the method comprising:
detecting one side of a body of the mobile terminal comes into contact with one side of an external terminal;
displaying, via a touchscreen of the mobile terminal, a first area corresponding to a contact area of the body and the external terminal and a second area including the content;
receiving, via a controller of the mobile terminal, an input of moving the content displayed in the second area to the first area;
displaying the content in the first area of the touchscreen; and
sharing, via the controller, the content in the first area with the external terminal.
